insert into partenaire values ("3771","29/07/2013","","","","","","ESOC 2013AA 22 novembre 2012, de la part de Liesa Ross - L_Ross@acs.org - message d'erreur sur cette adresse, meliesar@gmail.com - envoyer emails à cette adresseHello,I am the Marketing Manager for ACS Catalysis <http://www.pubs.acs.org/catalysis>  journal, and I would like to sponsor the following for ESOC 2013:· 3) Oral Communication Awards 2 000 €  (approx. 1,923.81 USD) - à mettre à jour sur le tableau· Symposium bag insert 350 € (approx. 448.89 USD) - à mettre à jour sur le tableauI would like to pay for these sponsorships in December. However, I am only permitted to pay less than 2,500 USD in 2012.  If the USD cost is 2,500 USD or more, I will not be able to pay for the sponsorship.The Good news… I would also like to sponsor the Programme for 1 500 €. - à mettre à jour sur le tableauSo please send me a January 2013 invoice for the Programme advertisement, and I will pay in early 2013.- à mettre à jour sur le tableau I hope I explained all of this clearly. If the arrangement is sufficient for you, I have attached the journal logos for your convenience. You may link the logo to www.acs.org/catalysis <http://www.acs.org/catalysis>Liesa Ross, Marketing Manager, ACS Publications1155 16th Street, NW, Washington, DC 20036 | 202-776-8219 | L_ross@acs.org | http://pubs.acs.org/  Oral Communication Awards                  2 000 €               Symposium Bag Inserts                350 €                 Renée John, 800-227-5558, ext 6286, r_john@acs.org                 Advertisement in the Final Programme/                1 500 €");
insert into partenaire values ("3772","29/07/2013","","","","","","ESOC 2013AA: De: Jean-Antoine Rodriguez <jean.rodriguez@univ-amu.fr>Date: Fri, 23 Nov 2012 10:02:02 +0100À: <sponsorsesoc2013@atout-org.com>Objet: Fwd: EurJOC and ESOCBonjour Christelle,pour information je vous fais suivre le message de l'editeur de journaux scientifiques tres importantes de chez Wiley qui demande la possibilite de participer au sponsoring en complement de Wiley. Nous pensons que sa proposition est acceptable dans la mesure ou Wiley confirme sa participation en tant que Sponsor Gold plus 6000 pour celebrer la serie Patai comme nous en avons parle au telephone, ce qui fera un total de 16000€. Je devrais avoir confirmation de cela la semaine prochaine. L'idee d'attribuer des livres aux posters est interessante, il faudra determiner combien, par contre il me semble que s'ils veulent 2 personnes il faudra leur demander de faire la publicite dans 2 journaux differents. Des que j'aurai des nouvelles de la participation de Wiley je reviendrai vers vous pour lui faire une reponse afin que vous preniez les choses en main. Bien cordialement. Jean.Sujet:	EurJOC and ESOCDate :	Thu, 22 Nov 2012 12:54:43 +0000De :	Ross, Haymo - Weinheim <hross@wiley.com>Pour :	'jean.rodriguez@univ-amu.fr' <jean.rodriguez@univ-amu.fr>Dear Jean,I understand that Wiley colleagues from our Chichester site are currently negotiating with Ilan Marek about sponsorship. You may be aware of these negotiations and if not, I know that Ilan is going to present the proposal at your meeting next week.I wonder if we could have an additional agreement: We could publish conference adverts in EurJOC (and maybe in other journals as well) and in return the admission fee for one or two editors would be waived. EurJOC could also sponsor poster prizes although rather than making a donation we would provide Wiley organic chemistry books.I look forward to hearing from you after your meeting.Best regards,HaymoDr. Haymo RossDeputy Editor: Angewandte ChemieEditor: EurJOCEditor: ChemistryOpenPhone: +49 (0)6201 606-313AS Gold sponsor, 10 000 €, stand de 9 m2. ");
